&lt;p&gt;Use the following code (&lt;a href="http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/newsreader/view_thread/171788"&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt;):  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;% Loads a data for the example &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;load&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;mandrill&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c"&gt;% Plots an image for the example &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c"&gt;% Inserts a colorbar. a handle is created &lt;/span&gt;
